        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The power of your faith suffuses your ki. When you select this feat, choose chaos, evil, good, or law. Your choice must match one of your deity's alignment components.</p>\n<p>When you cast the <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Ki Strike]{Ki Strike}</em> focus spell and damage a creature whose alignment is opposite your chosen alignment, you can choose for the <em>ki strike</em> damage to be of the chosen type.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you can substitute the damage from <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Ki Blast]{Ki Blast}</em> (or other ki spells that deal force damage, at the GM's discretion) with damage of your chosen alignment.</p>"
